                                <emph>kiplerni</emph>.</note>
                        <note xml:id="Job-037-fn5" type="footnote">An alternative translation of Job
                            37:22, added after the Hebrew expression <foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">או תאמר פשט ב׳ </foreign>
                            ‘or say a second interpretation’. | C: <emph>Čafondan aruv jel kelir
                                janyna Täŋriniŋ qorquvly syj</emph>. | QB: <emph>Čafondan aruv jel
                                kelir janyna Täŋriniŋ qorquvly syj</emph>. | ADub.III.84:
                                <emph>Cafondan balquv keledir qorqunclu Tenrige syj</emph>. <foreign
                                xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">פשט שני </foreign>
                            <emph>Cafondan jamɣur kelse qorqunclu Tenrige maḥtav</emph>. |
                            Kobeckaitė (2019): <emph>Syrttan altyn ḱeĺadir Tenriniń qorḥunčludur
                                syj</emph>.</note>
                    </app>
                </listApp>
